        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>April 17/73</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I thank you for your kind letter &amp; curious photograph.—<ref target="#foot.f1"/> I shall be much pleased to receive any further communication on domestic productions, but let me urge you not to send me anything valuable, unless you publish it elsewhere, for I am growing old &amp; know not whether I shall ever have strength &amp; time to continue my former researches.</p>
<p>Dear Sir | Yours very faithfully | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>

        

        

